    "reviews_sample": [
      {
        "review_id": "7357974587393097132",
        "review_title": "Too Narrow, But Great Design",
        "review_author": "Jasmin S",
        "review_source": "kidsfootlocker.com",
        "review_source_url": "http://c4.ugc.bazaarvoice.com/9055-en_us/349644/review/232413288/redirect.htm?ctc_referralType=Shopping&ctc_referralDescription=Google",
        "review_text": "The only reason why I gave this shoe a 3/5 is because my Toddler has a wide foot. Dunks are cute, have cute color schemes but fit extremely tight and narrow. It makes no sense to go up in size because now the shoe will have too much space in the front. I wish they made wide sizes and it’s also difficult to get them on our children’s foot without hurting them because we can’t adjust the laces. But I do appreciate a slip on sneaker as it makes it effortless for the parents. However, dunks took the slip on to another level. It’s almost impossible to get the sneaker on. Great design, great colors and you can almost match the parents sneakers also but just too narrow for me. Hopefully one day they create a wider size to fit for some big foot kids lol.",
